            <property name="styleSheet">
             <string notr="true">QLabel {
    color: rgb(80, 80, 80);                  /* soft dark gray */
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Roboto&quot;, sans-serif;
}</string>
            </property>
            <property name="text">
             <string>BJT CAPACITANCE CALCULATOR

Voltage differences:
VCB = VC - VB
VBE = VB - VE

Collector-base capacitance:
Cµ = CJC / (1 + VCB/VJC)^(1/3)

Base-emitter capacitance:
Cπ = τF(IC/VT) + CJE / (1 - VBE/VJE)^(1/3)

Small-signal base resistance:
rπ = βVT / IC</string>
            </property>
            <property name="wordWrap">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
